                    government. Waynesbor graduates include: D. Rodes Massie, Latin, French, and
                    Mathematics; Charles H. Withrow, Greek, Spanish, Chemistry, and Moral
                    Philosophy; Robert T. Massie, Mixed Mathematics, Chemistry, Moral Philosophy; W.
                    H. H. Lynn, Moral Philosophy</summary>
